>>NOORY: With that
technology, too.

00:01:07.890 --> 00:01:10.850 align:middle line:84%
>>BENNETT: With that
technology, too, yes.

00:01:10.850 --> 00:01:12.450 align:middle line:90%
But it got me really enthused.

00:01:12.450 --> 00:01:14.190 align:middle line:84%
And I think every
human being in history

00:01:14.190 --> 00:01:17.550 align:middle line:84%
